<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='119960' id='t-119960'>you don't smoke, you always do service,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='122360' id='t-122360'>you're a good kid.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='124360' id='t-124360'>Some of the rules we had were strict,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='127960' id='t-127960'>but you followed the rules
