<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='147520' id='t-147520'>including myself.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='148760' id='t-148760'>From paper routes and babysitting,
I donated 10 percent.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='152720' id='t-152720'>I was the kind of religious
