<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='183960' id='t-183960'>This was where I felt safe.
This is certainty and clarity about life.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='188200' id='t-188200'>I had help raising my little daughter.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='190480' id='t-190480'>So that's why I accepted without question
that only men can lead,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='195400' id='t-195400'>and I accepted without question</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='197560' id='t-197560'>that women can't have the spiritual
